iate it with the presenter.</p>\n<p>BTW that <em>still</em> doesn't seem like a three-party model, because you don't have a meaningful Holder -- the Holder is just a store-and-forward relay for the credential, doesn't have an actual role in the protocol.  Even if you ignore replay, it's a two-party model.</p>",
